  "Constitution": {
    "_type": "text",
    "content": "DRAFT\n• Draft order determined by Playoff and Loser Bowl results\n• Divisions randomly determined each year at draft\n• Keepers: From 4th Round on, every player drafted the previous year is eligible\n• Rule changes voted on at draft each year\n\nSTACKED BONUS\n• 3-point stacked bonus: QB throwing TD to same-team receiver, TE, or RB\n\nFEES & PAYOUTS\n• Entry Fee: $500/team\n• 1st Place: 70%   |   2nd Place: 20%   |   3rd Place: 10%\n• Division Winners: $100 each\n• Most Points (season): $100\n• Best Record: $100\n\nROSTER\n• IR slot: Removed\n\nPLAYOFFS\n• 8-Team Playoff — Weeks 15–17\n• Top 3 per division seeded 1–3; remaining spots filled by best record\n• Reseeded each round (highest seed vs. lowest seed)\n\nLOSER BOWL\n• 4 non-playoff teams compete to determine draft picks 1–6\n\n2026 RULE\n• Team with least total points (including playoffs) pays for trophy engraving & shipping"
  }
